      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-4 mb-6">How to Build a Mobile App for a Supplement Brand</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8">Supplement brands thrive on retention and repeat purchases. But many are struggling with a heavy reliance on email, SMS, and expensive paid ads. This guide shows how to create a high-performing mobile app with MobiLoud and unlock a new channel for loyalty and LTV, without reinventing your tech stack.</p>
